{"tid":1858131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑色五毛分化警告！！分別扮演反罷工既醫護 vs 詛咒反罷工既非醫護","createTime":"2020-02-02T13:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T14:40:19.000Z","uid":253320,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"14672492aa5770444c0b55fba2ab64d5b2e39bce","tid":1858131,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:44:54.000Z","msg":"反罷工既醫護:<br />\n1. 醫護天職<br />\n2. 有自己方法救人<br />\n3. 政治不要凌駕救護<br />\n<br />\n詛咒反罷工既非醫護:<br />\n1. 唔罷工就係仆街垃圾, 不盡醫護天職, 令醫護人員受盡冷言冷語<br />\n2. 唔封關就咩方法都係錯, 封關係唯一方法, 令封關變得非理性, 抹黑罷工<br />\n3. 政治真的凌駕救護, 代入五大訴求, 令醫護人士進退不能, 心灰意冷<br />\n<br />\n建議:<br />\n1. 非醫護人士不要把對抗政府既責任全部交給醫護, 想想自己能做什麼, 包括發起自己界別既工業行動。<br />\n2. 理性思考政府不封關, 有沒有其他方法阻止大陸人來港。<br />\n3. 先不要代入五大訴求, 依個唔係支線任, 唔係天時地利, 係香港同全球災難。"},{"pid":"7a59acdd704fcedddeaa7f9a64f91ca771b7aa01","tid":1858131,"uid":52566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QuCAdCJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuCAdCJ.png&h=e289bf78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8d4df43fd6923c8a1e245e5ea9549272b358168","tid":1858131,"uid":159916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"recommendation: quit lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1f487271078d803f1287f0ff91aea332c84a2c","tid":1858131,"uid":2300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:47:09.000Z","msg":"撐罷工，真係罷先好，唔撚洗理lihkg d post 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3008e7b6f5c64eaddd6c310f60eaef9b0c0f06a7","tid":1858131,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f1f487271078d803f1287f0ff91aea332c84a2c","tid":1858131,"uid":2300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:47:09.000Z","msg":"撐罷工，真係罷先好，唔撚洗理lihkg d post 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/ln